2.00	Pardesi_(1957_film)	Journey Beyond Three Seas	Journey Beyond Three Seas (Hindi: ; Russian: ) is a 1957 Indian-Soviet popular film, jointly directed by Khwaja Ahmad Abbas and Vasili Pronin. It was made in two version, Hindi and Russian, and is based on the travelogues of Russian traveller Afanasy Nikitin, called A Journey Beyond the Three Seas, which is now considered a Russian literary monument.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/8/8c/Pardesi_%281957%29.jpg
